::The Eletors::

Element nods, kneeling down at putting Prowl on the ground. He then 
proceeds to split up into the Eletors. Mantle steps forward, the 
others standing back.

"Hello, my name is Mantle and this is my team," he says, gesturing 
behind him, "We're a group of Maximals that were with Striker's 
group, and we've been looking for him. Have you seen Striker or his 
group?"

>

like a
